The paper involves the use of deep learning for visual search tasks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). It also evaluates the interaction between humans and the deep learning system, which relates to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The use of deep learning also falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper involves the analysis of eye-movements, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR).
